<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٦٠٦٨ - عَنِ الأَسْوَدِ عَنْ عَائِشَةَ.<span class="c5"> قالت:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>